5781,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287b5421cffepKtWCnuNTsxy0u\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d784b2ab3001MZscGP5ogeK7WL\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d784b18cb0019nqZuLWh6SC9xe\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287b5421cffepKtWCnuNTsxy0u\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Now I'll create the scaffold for AR-002 following the AR-001 convention.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775839685779,\"end\":1775839685779}}}\n  Line 22: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775839724848,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287b5421cffepKtWCnuNTsxy0u\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d784b532c001pg0Ys22xGR7L5g\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d784b18cb0019nqZuLWh6SC9xe\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287b5421cffepKtWCnuNTsxy0u\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_a7e19d9c79ff4125b0e0e93f\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 Tasks\\n\\n**Module:** pkg/apis  \\n**Language:** Go  \\n**Size:** S  \\n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design completed)\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Phase 1: Scaffold & Registration\\n\\n- [ ] **1.1** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/` directory structure\\n- [ ] **1.2** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/register.go` - register API group\\n- [ ] **1.3** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/register.go` - define `SchemeGroupVersion`, `SchemeBuilder`, `AddToScheme`\\n- [ ] **1.4** Create `pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/doc.go` - add Go package documentation\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Phase 2: Type Definitions\\n\\n- [ ] **2.1** Define `CodeInterpreterPhase` enum (Pending, Running, Failed, Terminating)\\n- [ ] **2.2** Define `CodeInterpreterCondition` struct (type, status, reason, message, lastTransitionTime)\\n- [ ] **2.3** Define `KernelSpec` struct (language, image, resources)\\n- [ ] **2.4** Define `SessionConfig` struct (timeout, idleTimeout, maxSessions)\\n- [ ] **2.5** Define `SecurityPolicy` struct (allowedPackages, blockedOperations, networkAccess)\\n- [ ] **2.6** Define `CodeInterpreterSpec` struct (kernel, session, security, resources)\\n- [ ] **2.7** Define `CodeInterpreterStatus` struct (phase, conditions, activeSessions, startTime, lastTransitionTime)\\n- [ ] **2.8** Define `CodeInterpreter` struct (TypeMeta, ObjectMeta, Spec, Status)\\n- [ ] **2.9** Define `CodeInterpreterList` struct (TypeMeta, ListMeta, Items)\\n- [ ] **2.10** Add JSON tags (camelCase) and protobuf tags to all types\\n- [ ] **2.11** Implement `runtime.Object` interface for CodeInterpreter and CodeInterpreterList\\n\\n---\\n\\n## Phase 3: Defaults & Validation\\n...\n  Line 26: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775839761065,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287b5421cffepKtWCnuNTsxy0u\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d784bd427001n6dS1g8ovMnnoZ\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d784bc56a001ht1Gs2u6AItIVr\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287b5421cffepKtWCnuNTsxy0u\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_ab50dc56a2d94a8088ecf95a\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# Proposal: AR-002 — CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\\n\\n## Purpose\\n\\nDefine the `CodeInterpreter` Custom Resource Definition (CRD) and associated types for the AgentCube platform. This CRD enables users to declare and manage code interpreter configurations as Kubernetes-native resources, providing isolated kernel environments for AI agent code execution.\\n\\nThe `CodeInterpreter` resource represents a configurable code execution environment with support for:\\n- Multiple kernel languages (Python, R, Julia, etc.)\\n- Session management and lifecycle\\n- Security policies (package allowlists, operation restrictions)\\n- Resource quotas (CPU, memory per session)\\n- Status tracking (phase, conditions, active sessions)\\n\\n## Scope\\n\\n**Module:** `pkg/apis`  \\n**API Group:** `codeinterpreter.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`  \\n**Kind:** `CodeInterpreter` (namespaced)  \\n**Size:** S\\n\\n### In Scope\\n\\n1. **Type Definitions** (`pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/types.go`)\\n   - `CodeInterpreter` - main resource struct\\n   - `CodeInterpreterSpec` - desired state specification\\n   - `CodeInterpreterStatus` - observed state status\\n   - `KernelSpec` - kernel configuration (language, image, resources)\\n   - `SessionConfig` - session timeout and limits\\n   - `SecurityPolicy` - package allowlists and operation restrictions\\n   - `CodeInterpreterPhase` - lifecycle phase enum\\n   - `CodeInterpreterCondition` - status conditions\\n\\n2. **API Registration** (`pkg/apis/codeinterpreter/v1alpha1/register.go`)\\n   - `SchemeGroupVersion` definition\\n   - `SchemeBuilder` registration\\n   - `AddToScheme` function\\n   - `Resource` and `Kind` helpers\\n\\n3. **CRD Man...\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z_logs/AR-001_ST-5.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775839142628,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287bd30b5ffeEecEG6tiobwWrM\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7842de32001yoFnTPTbh3qBWi\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7842d026001yAs5Djz39AJYdK\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287bd30b5ffeEecEG6tiobwWrM\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I'll implement the AgentRuntime CRD type definition for the agentcube project. Let me first explore the project structure and specifications.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775839142626,\"end\":1775839142626}}}\n  Line 5: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775839143224,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287bd30b5ffeEecEG6tiobwWrM\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7842e37f001ulmZBHtopPHcQn\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7842d026001yAs5Djz39AJYdK\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287bd30b5ffeEecEG6tiobwWrM\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"glob\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-383afb187cd84da18e46c5cf1af6cd44\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"**/spec*.md\"},\"output\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-001/spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/integrations/spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/sandbox-orchestration/spec.md\\n/home/dsj/benchma