e\",\"timestamp\":1775839150624,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287bd30b5ffeEecEG6tiobwWrM\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7842fbee001DDP3O3urrPNFQy\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7842f444001dtX8TH1u33Vn9L\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287bd30b5ffeEecEG6tiobwWrM\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-f1965ddd9644422f8783f20018eddad2\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-001/delta-spec.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-001/delta-spec.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-001 Delta Specification: CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\\n2: \\n3: ## Purpose\\n4: \\n5: Define Go type definitions and Kubernetes CRD registration for the `AgentRuntime` custom resource in the `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API group, including integration with the generated client-go library and proper API machinery support.\\n6: \\n7: ## Requirements\\n8: \\n9: ### Requirement: AgentRuntime type metadata and API group version\\n10: \\n11: The system SHALL define `AgentRuntime` as a Kubernetes custom resource with `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` API group, `v1alpha1` version, kind `AgentRuntime`, and resource plural `agentruntimes`.\\n12: \\n13: #### Scenario: Type metadata reflects GVR mapping\\n14: - **GIVEN** a Kubernetes API server resolving the CRD type\\n15: - **WHEN** the `TypeMeta` fields are inspected\\n16: - **THEN** `APIVersion` is `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` and `Kind` is `AgentRuntime`\\n17: \\n18: #### Scenario: Resource plural matches client-go expectations\\n19: - **GIVEN** a typed client for `AgentRuntime`\\n20: - **WHEN** constructing a `GroupVersionResource` from the type\\n21: - **THEN** resource name is `agentruntimes` in plural form\\n22: \\n23: ### Requirement: AgentRuntimeSpec structure with required fields\\n24: \\n25: The system SHALL define `AgentRuntimeSpec` struct with required fields: `PodT...\n  Line 113: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775839658267,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287bd30b5ffeEecEG6tiobwWrM\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d784ac0fa001fgRWqc7zS1St4J\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d784a7c4e001BIaVwIfP5HFb4G\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287bd30b5ffeEecEG6tiobwWrM\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"write\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-4bbcf0ebedb64c3db6cbabc947d0f823\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"content\":\"# AgentCube Runtime API\\n\\nThis package contains the Kubernetes API definitions for the AgentCube runtime resources.\\n\\n## API Group\\n\\n- **Group**: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\\n- **Version**: `v1alpha1`\\n- **Kind**: `AgentRuntime`\\n\\n## Types\\n\\n### AgentRuntime\\n\\n`AgentRuntime` is a Kubernetes custom resource that defines a sandbox orchestration runtime for managing the lifecycle of agent pods.\\n\\n#### Spec\\n\\nThe `AgentRuntimeSpec` defines the desired state of an AgentRuntime:\\n\\n- **PodTemplate** (*SandboxTemplate, required): Template for creating sandbox pods\\n- **SessionTimeout** (*metav1.Duration, optional): Timeout for idle sessions before cleanup (default: 15m)\\n- **MaxSessionDuration** (*metav1.Duration, optional): Maximum allowed duration for a session (default: 8h)\\n\\n#### Status\\n\\nThe `AgentRuntimeStatus` defines the observed state of an AgentRuntime:\\n\\n- **Conditions** ([]metav1.Condition, optional): List of conditions representing the runtime state\\n- **ObservedGeneration** (int64, optional): Most recent generation observed by the controller\\n\\n### SandboxTemplate\\n\\nDefines the template for creating sandbox pods:\\n\\n- **Metadata** (*SandboxMetadata, optional): Labels and annotations for the pod\\n- **Spec** (SandboxPodSpec, required): Pod specification\\n\\n### SandboxPodSpec\\n\\nDefines the pod specification for sandbox pods:\\n\\n- **Containers** ([]SandboxContainer, required): List of containers in the pod\\n- **NodeSelector** (map[string]string, optional): Node selection constraints\\n- **Affinity** (*SandboxAffinity, optional): Pod scheduling constraints\\n- **Tolerations** ([]SandboxToleration,...\n  Line 116: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775839666997,\"sessionID\":\"ses_287bd30b5ffeEecEG6tiobwWrM\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d784ae312001Wpcfr2BoW9T8jr\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d784ac1500015DmpKHfVGp3dOk\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_287bd30b5ffeEecEG6tiobwWrM\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"edit\",\"callID\":\"toolu_tool-09b9ab35e0f348f0b3432e83ea2a2245\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-001/README.md\",\"newString\":\"# AR-001 Implementation Notes\\n\\n## Implementation Status\\n- [x] Spec definition\\n- [x] Go type definitions\\n- [x] CRD registration\\n- [x] Tests\\n- [x] Documentation\\n\\n## Implementation Details\\n\\n### Files Created\\n\\n1. **pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go**: Complete Go type definitions for AgentRuntime CRD\\n2. **pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go**: Scheme registration and API group configuration\\n3. **pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go**: Package documentation and kubebuilder markers\\n4. **pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/deepcopy.go**: DeepCopy methods for all types\\n5. **pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go**: Comprehensive unit tests (32 test cases)\\n6. **config/crd/bases/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml**: CRD YAML definition\\n7. **pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/README.md**: Package documentation and usage examples\\n\\n### Test Coverage\\n\\nAll 32 unit tests pass, covering:\\n- Type metadata and API group version\\n- Spec structure and default values\\n- Status conditions\\n- List type operations\\n- JSON serialization/deserialization\\n- Scheme registration\\n- All sandbox configuration types (containers, volumes, probes, affinity, tolerations, security contexts)\\n- DeepCopy functionality\\n\\n### API Contract\\n