imi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md`.\\n\\nThe proposal includes all the requested sections:\\n\\n1. **Purpose** — Defines the `AgentRuntime` CRD types to enable Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration for AI agent workloads\\n\\n2. **Scope** — \\n   - In scope: Package structure, API group (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`), types defined, scheme registration, kubebuilder markers, code generation, and generated client surface\\n   - Out of scope: CodeInterpreter CRD, Workload Manager HTTP API, reconciler logic, Helm chart rendering, RBAC\\n\\n3. **Design** — File layout, type definitions (AgentRuntime, AgentRuntimeSpec, AgentRuntimeStatus, shared types), scheme registration, and code generation pipeline\\n\\n4. **Impact analysis** — Files created, files generated, downstream consumers (client-go, Workload Manager, Helm charts), and breaking change risk assessment\\n\\n5. **Alternatives considered** — Four alternatives analyzed:\\n   - Standalone CRD YAML (no Go types) — rejected\\n   - Kubebuilder/controller-runtime scaffolding — rejected  \\n   - Multi-version API from day one — rejected\\n   - Embed full `corev1.PodTemplateSpec` — rejected\\n\\n6. **Dependencies** and **Verification** sections are also included\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775839097484,\"end\":1775839097484}}}\n\n(Results truncated: showing 100 of 521 matches (421 hidden). Consider using a more specific path or pattern.)","metadata":{"matches":521,"truncated":true},"title":"AR-001|AgentRuntime.*CRD","time":{"start":1775839818593,"end":1775839818658}}}}
